data.description: Come see your dream home at 11641 Claudette Street. Boasting 4-bedrooms, and 2-bathrooms this immaculately maintained home is a true gem! Upon entering you are greeted by the living area and kitchen. The kitchen features granite counter-tops, plenty of cabinet space, recessed lighting and an open view to the rest of the home. Nice sized owner's retreat with a shower/bathtub combination. Sizeable rooms, bathrooms and closets. Carpet and easy to maintain luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout home. The spacious backyard is an entertainers dream with lots of space, and privacy wood fencing. Convenient access to Lackland Air Force Base, major highways, schools, dining and shopping.
